metadata.name: FIANNA THE SUMMONER
metadata.description:
"O mighty Dragon please answer my prayers and come before me!"

Fianna the summoner has completed her very first ritual.She has summoned the mighty Dragon "Naga".

Naga is a very rare water dragon for the summoner to summon.the other summoners that witness the ritual still cannot believe their eyes.

Maybe Fianna is a chosen one....?
